                <h2>About Our Library</h2>
                <p>Welcome to the Aror University Library!</p>
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>At Aror University Library, our mission is to provide a comprehensive collection of resources and services to support the teaching, learning, and research needs of our university community. We strive to create a welcoming and inclusive environment that promotes academic success and personal growth.</p>
                <h3>On-Site and Online Borrowing</h3>
                <p>Our library offers both on-site and online borrowing facilities to ensure that our patrons have access to the materials they need, wherever they are. Whether you prefer to visit us in person or access our resources remotely, we are here to support your academic endeavors.</p>
                <h3>Collection Highlights</h3>
                <p>Our collection includes a wide range of print and electronic resources, including books, journals, databases, and multimedia materials. We continuously update our collection to reflect the evolving needs of our users and to support the latest research and scholarship.</p>
                <h3>Services and Facilities</h3>
                <p>In addition to our borrowing facilities, we offer a variety of services and facilities to enhance your library experience. These include computer workstations, group study rooms, interlibrary loan services, and research assistance from our knowledgeable librarians.</p>
                <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                <p>We are here to help! If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us. You can reach us by phone, email, or visit us in person during our opening hours.</p>
                <p>Thank you for choosing Aror University Library. We look forward to serving you!</p>
